    {
      "segment_id": "call1_8",
      "text": "Okay, fine sir. Sir, I am Dr. Farana. I want to do a video verification for your Tata AI policy. In this, I will ask verification and medical history questions. This call will be recorded for quality and audit purposes. And this will take 5 to 10 minutes to complete this call.",
