      "call_index": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "call1_9",
      "text": "Please kindly note that your responses and replies regarding your health and habits will become part of your insurance policy. And if this proposal form is accepted, it will become a legal document between you and Tata AI. So, if there is any incorrect answer or response, there are chances of the policy being cancelled before or after issuance. Later on, there are also chances of rejection at the time of claiming. So, I request you to answer my questions completely and correctly, okay?",
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "start_timestamp": "0:31",
      "end_timestamp": "0:55",
      "call_index": 1
    },
    {
